snippet.title: Super Metroid Redesign (SNES Gameplay)
snippet.description:
Super Metroid Redesign is a total overhaul of Super Metroid. The Planet Zebes, now bigger than we've previously seen it, is filled with many mysteries. Sleeping within the depths of the planet is a secret heavily protected by the last standing symbols of the great Chozo race.

Read more at https://goo.gl/cuGjWX
